<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A6304022001" page = "1">
<title>
Voltage Check
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove instrument cluster panel. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9306001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check for voltage at each terminal with connectors connected to the P/S control module.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
As each terminal voltage is affected by the battery voltage, confirm if the battery voltage is 12 V or more when ignition is ON.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Voltage with asterisk (*) cannot be measured with voltmeter because it is pulse signal. Use oscilloscope for its check.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
</s1>
